# Documentation Rules

| Doc | Owns |
|---|---|
| PRD.md | Product behavior |
| Architecture.md | Technical structure (v2 Inabiya only — no LMS) |
| Rules.md | Engineering law |
| Phases.md | Delivery sequence |
| Design.md | Visual systems A/B |
| Memory.md | Live progress |

## When editing

- Keep docs consistent with locked stack
- Prefer Memory for progress; do not duplicate PRD into Memory
- Architecture changes that affect coding need Rules/Phases sync if sequencing/stack shifts
- Never reintroduce Student/Admission/Hostel education domains
